_sText:
Note: This is simply a re-upload of an older map by me, now with a new name. Re-uploaded since I shut down my older account.


This map was originally created by me as one of my first maps, for a gaming night at my school. It hasn't been touched since, and most likely never will. It was originally named "fy_noname_beta", seeing how I couldn't come up with a name, but now, still out of creativity, I decided to call it "netnat", the danish word for "gaming night".


Has a whole lot of spawns, too...
